# Protocol auto-copy

Every response MUST use the `═══ … ═══ END ═══` wrapper (see `600-protocol.mdc`).

The hook `.cursor/hooks/copy_cassandra_protocol.py` copies that block to clipboard
automatically after each agent turn. Do not paste a second copy outside the markers.

User-global hook also lives at `~/.cursor/hooks/copy_protocol_block.py` for non-Cassandra windows.
